title: "BLACK SEA — Special Investigation Unit / CID"
abstract: >-
  An all-source investigative-analyst skill for Claude Code and other SKILL.md agents. Produces
  standardized, confidence-graded intelligence dossiers on organizations and people — org & financial
  forensics, competitor & market intelligence, and gated due-diligence person profiling — under a
  Prime Directive that forbids fabrication.
